sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Frontend UI
    participant API as tRPC API
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant Encrypt as Encryption Service
    participant DB as Database
    participant Audit as Audit Logger

    User->>UI: Open Create Secret form
    UI->>Auth: Check session
    Auth-->>UI: Session valid
    User->>UI: Enter name and content
    UI->>API: secrets.create
    API->>Auth: validateSession
    Auth-->>API: userId, orgId
    API->>DB: checkSecretLimit
    DB-->>API: ok
    API->>Encrypt: encrypt data with key
    Encrypt-->>API: encryptedData
    API->>DB: INSERT Secret
    DB-->>API: secretId
    API->>Audit: log create event
    Audit->>DB: INSERT SecretAccessLog
    API-->>UI: success
    UI-->>User: Secret created
